{"tid":404183,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"（背脊向天食得）澳洲袋鼠泛濫　向中國人推銷上餐桌","createTime":"2017-09-17T23:59:32.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-18T07:33:47.000Z","uid":41351,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"4b5feda660f021cca5742f83d8afa949198a36c9","tid":404183,"uid":41351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-17T23:59:32.000Z","msg":"丹麥生蠔泛濫、荷蘭的小龍蝦泛濫、北美的螃蟹泛濫......現在，連澳洲的袋鼠也泛濫成災，也一樣準備送上門給中國人享用！<br />\n《北青網》報導，據澳洲官方數據統計，袋鼠在2010年時只有2700萬隻，目前已爆增至近4500萬隻，比該國人口總數多出一倍。新南威爾斯省的地主稱，袋鼠數目近年激增，牠們破壞圍欄、與家畜爭奪食物及水、踐踏農作物。袋鼠甚至危及到交通安全，成為對當地司機威脅最大的動物。<br />\n環境生態學專家指，在塔斯曼尼亞虎滅絕後，澳洲野狗也瀕臨滅絕，袋鼠幾乎處於無天敵的狀態。科學家警告必須採取措施加以控制袋鼠的數量，澳政府決定對袋鼠下達捕殺令，有澳洲人和學者則呼籲本國人，考慮多吃袋鼠肉。<br />\n其實，吃袋鼠肉在當地歷史悠久。澳洲土著過去就經常食用袋鼠肉，尤其喜歡美味的烤袋鼠尾巴。歷史學家Barbara Santich在著作《大膽的口味》裡寫道：作為澳洲的美食遺產，袋鼠食譜經常出現在烹飪書裏，將袋鼠肉與鹹豬肉一起燉的袋鼠湯，曾備受推崇。<br />\n直到20世紀30年代，隨著越來越多的澳洲人移居城市，人民生活水平的提高，袋鼠肉等所謂的「叢林食物」才漸漸失寵，許多澳洲人甚至認為，吃袋鼠肉是「不愛國」的行為。雖然袋鼠肉會作為食品出售，不過有95%都會出口至海外。<br />\n近來，丹麥、荷蘭和北美陸續傳出生蠔、龍蝦、螃蟹泛濫成災，中國網民都笑稱讓中國「吃貨」前去「消災」。澳洲人確實已開始向中國人推銷袋鼠肉，去年5月10日，澳洲首批袋鼠肉樣品就被送到中國供「試吃」。<br />\n澳水利與農業部部長助理麥克唐納博士說，澳洲很多華人餐館裡都可以吃到袋鼠肉，還有一名著名的華人廚師，用小袋鼠烹製了一道當地名菜。因此，袋鼠肉完全符合中國人的口味和烹飪方法。據介紹，一般來說，袋鼠肉和牛肉價錢差不多，或者比牛肉貴一點，是種比較高檔的食物，未來很可能出現在中國的高檔餐廳。<br />\n不少中國網友看到有關消息後，紛紛表示：「我願為保持生態平衡，做出貢獻。」「這大概是國寶圈子裡混得最差的了吧。」「你們竟然吃鼠鼠，牠那麼可愛。」「是想把牠吃成怎麼個級別？珍稀？瀕危？博物館還是書上？」「直接生吃行嗎？」「應該也是先切塊，料酒去腥，然後大火......」。　<br />\n<a href=\"http://m.appledaily.com.tw/realtimenews/article/international/20170918/1205811/papersec_right\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.appledaily.com.tw%2Frealtimenews%2Farticle%2Finternational%2F20170918%2F1205811%2Fpapersec_right&d=dfVp40sK0uRlKjoKzgMyZZ4f2li5K%2Fs6EGgmwhpeblA%3D&h=9edb79d1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://m.appledaily.com.tw/realtimenews/article/international/20170918/1205811/papersec_right</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/18/075804_0f2c9874e7ad48ce0bf3de700bd30bb1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F18%2F075804_0f2c9874e7ad48ce0bf3de700bd30bb1.jpg&h=254acdaf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n支那人真係出晒名雜食"},{"pid":"4f5842ac7691ba9354cb88c06b1cce60133a39dd","tid":404183,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T00:08:52.000Z","msg":"咁邊個食支蛆？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"002e8ca797159c6eceb18a416f80f3a889f0880c","tid":404183,"uid":47966,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T00:11:24.000Z","msg":"今年美食節有間賣袋鼠肉扒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e4c920cbb5c986a5cfcc2ccd75e06c26638d229","tid":404183,"uid":143582,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T00:12:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>今年美食節有間賣袋鼠肉扒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n澳洲大把啦"},{"pid":"155a06972769cf29d3a41c7d3923d7b6f6e3723b","tid":404183,"uid":37735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T03:13:15.000Z","msg":"澳洲個生態 根本要推到重建<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"21143cd148b0ee5eec614cd328d553e406013cc9","tid":404183,"uid":127123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T03:19:46.000Z","msg":"袋鼠肉的口感和牛肉有點相似，沒有牛肉吃起來嫩，而且羶味很重。<br />\n<br />\n又臭又酸酸地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f556bc4f78a9a7abea53c70b4161e6ddd7c9647","tid":404183,"uid":23170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T03:34:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>今年美食節有間賣袋鼠肉扒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n澳洲大把啦</blockquote><br />\n其實周街都已經有得買<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a89323176c014a657137d2112e6530dd242896a","tid":404183,"uid":70085,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T03:36:26.000Z","msg":"之前喺澳洲買咗塊煎，太羶食咗幾舊扔咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d1afb8ecf7b9101ead2071119215e074698d767","tid":404183,"uid":15954,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T03:36:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>袋鼠肉的口感和牛肉有點相似，沒有牛肉吃起來嫩，而且羶味很重。<br />\n<br />\n又臭又酸酸地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n仲要貴d"},{"pid":"0f771b11f0ebc0909967fbbec78ae247ad33d323","tid":404183,"uid":14103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T03:38:06.000Z","msg":"澳洲不嬲都食袋鼠架啦"},{"pid":"87b611b1d7b0c5148ed3c20a0448b133d0ce9d5d","tid":404183,"uid":1646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T03:38:58.000Z","msg":"係澳洲比人當劣食<br />\n<br />\n所以要推比支那人食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"20bc048be15255e2624befb7fc697e6b61a11efa","tid":404183,"uid":54181,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T03:39:14.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b1986d43353be45a4a99eb323250d1d2ecd83de2","tid":404183,"uid":49392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T03:44:55.000Z","msg":"用袋鼠好打得既形象做宣傳，吹到好似虎鞭咁咪得"},{"pid":"4826d988fc90dd4ca64f3031048aa0e44625adf2","tid":404183,"uid":121580,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T03:52:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>今年美食節有間賣袋鼠肉扒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/nor